    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the art and architecture that coincided with the reign of Murad V, who ruled briefly in 1876. The sultan was deposed quickly due to signs of mental instability.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000026081/Levey, World of Ottoman Art (1975)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de kunst en architectuur in de periode van de heerschappij van Moerad V, die kort geregeerde in 1876. De sultan werd snel afgezet als gevolg van tekenen van geestelijke instabiliteit.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052378/Winkler Prins Encyclopedie (1990)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>用來表示與穆拉德五世統治時期有關的藝術與建築。穆拉德五世僅在西元 1876 年進行為期短暫的統治，由於他出現精神不穩定的徵兆，因此很快便遭到罷免。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
